About this game
Dogfight jet fighters rule the sky!

Dogfight is absolutely FREE to download!

Easy one finger control and your jet plane will do the rest

Gun down enemy jet fighters using your miniguns and air-to-air missiles

Perform air acrobatics to hunt down enemy jet fighters and drop them off in mid-air.

Unlock cool new jet planes

Discover new and exciting weapons

Complete level missions and earn your medals

Action packed, fast adrenaline rush dogfight to keep you going for days! The game is one of the top action jet fighter shooter wargames you will find in 2020/2021!
